data.description: The pleasures of country space with the convenience of city life.(2.7% assumable loan option!!) This home has massive front and back yards. Th split plan features large bedrooms for everyone with wonderful closet space. The kitchen opens into the family room with a large bar for quick meals or entertainment. These motivated sellers Are leaving behind the new stainless steel kitchen appliances! The beautiful hardwood floors in the living room accent the wood burning fireplace. The living French doors open to the covered patio overlooking the fenced, shaded backyard. The backyard has a storage building and a wired workshop that’s perfect for anyone that works on cars or motorcycles! Call your favorite Realtor for a showing.
